# Normalise line endings to LF in the working tree on every platform.
# Without this, Git-for-Windows' default `core.autocrlf=true` checks
# the captured wire / snapshot fixtures out with CRLF, and the
# `snapshot_traces` test (which generates `\n`) fails on Windows CI
# with byte-for-byte-identical-looking diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf
